abstract: >-
  Python library for radio astronomy data processing and visualization
  for the Owens Valley Radio Observatory - Long Wavelength Array (OVRO-LWA).
  Provides unified data loading from local/S3/DOI sources, FITS to Zarr
  conversion, and interactive visualization tools.
